\v 25 Ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, in apa kupan, piraov…®n k…®rik aik…®n, nhag…®n e Rehab. In piraov…®n kape swatuk, m…ôr…®g Kughen r…®m…®ni m…ô in pian atuatuk tuk norien huv…ô yame in r…®mnor. K…®ni wok e in e yame r…®mnor:\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Hib 11:31\x* n…®p…®g k…®mnher-p…ôn k…®n yem…ô Isrel mir k…®raru m…ô tukw…ôm-…ôsaah ap…®s-ap…®s ye Jeriko, Rehab r…®mn…ôhit…ô ye kafan nim…ô tuk …ôriu, mher-p…ôn k…®n …ôriu kwaiyu kar…®n m…®rarer…®g.\f + \fr 2:25 \ft  ∆émru stori kape Rehab ye Jos 2.\f*   
\p
\v 26 N…®prai yermam…ô, tukm…ô nanm…®n r…ôta iran, r…®mamh…ô. K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, nhat…ôt…ôyen yame r…®p…ôh n…®ku…ôyen k…®n norien huv…ô m…®n…ô, nagheen r…®rk…ôk r…ômhen k…®n yame r…®mamh…ô.   
\c 3  
\s1 N…ôgkiarien kape yermam…ô m…®ne kafan norien  
\p
\v 1 Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô. R…®p…ôh n…®huv…ôyen m…ô k…®mi…ô khapsaah takhau…ô n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô kape nim…ôhuak, meinai nakharkun m…ô Kughen In tukr…ôm huv…ô m…ôkir n…®mraghien m…®ne n…ôgkiarien kape n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô rapita yame tukr…ôkir n…®mraghien m…®ne n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô apnap…®g,  
\v 2 meinai k…®taw…ô m…®fam tukham…®r ye n…®mraghien kap…ôtaw…ô n…®p…®g r…®psaah. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô yermam…ô k…®rik ramehu…ô ye neram…®n, ramhajoun p…ôn m…ô in yermam…ô atuatuk k…®rik, k…®ni r…®rkun nehu…ôyen ye n…®pran m…®n…ô fam …ôgk…ôp.  
\v 3 Ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, kamruk-p…ôn braedel ye n…ôkwai hos m…ô in tukror n…ôr…®gien kape yermam…ô. Kam…ôk…ôkin kap…ôn kap…ô hos, k…®ni raukreik…®n n…®pran m…®n…ô fam.  
\v 4 K…®ni bot, in nar ehu…ô k…®rik. K…®ni n…®m…ôtag ehu…ô ramr…ôh, m…ôr…®g stia in nar k…ôsk…ôh k…®rik yame n…®p…®g kapten ramarar-arar iran, k…®ni n…®prai bot m…®n…ô fam ramiko-p…ôn a kapten rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®v…ôn p…ôn ik…®n.  
\v 5 Ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, neram…® jir in nar k…ôsk…ôh k…®rik, m…ôr…®g r…®rkun n…®vi-p…ônien nar ehu…ô m…®n…ô. R…®kimi…ô tukr…ôs…®k m…®n ru kw…ôn…ômtarh ye nap in nar k…ôsk…ôh k…®rik m…ôr…®g r…®rkun nu…ôk-p…ônien m…ôs nai r…®psaah.  
\v 6 K…®ni n…ôfrak…®sien, neram…® jir in r…ômhen k…®n nap yame Setan ramhitg…®n-p…ôn nap iran. Neram…® jir in nor…® yermam…ô yame ramor norien has m…®n…ô fam kape tokrei tan…ô. K…®ni nahasien m…®n…ô fam kafan kasoriah narmam…ô, masoriah swatuk m…®n…ô fam ye n…®mraghien fam kape narmam…ô.  
\v 7-8 Nehu…ôyen ye neram…® jir in r…ômhen k…®n norien yepou ye nar aparu p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô m…ô tuks…ôpou. In e nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô, m…®ne man m…®n…ô, m…®ne nar m…®ragh yam…ô m…®ne kaserko, m…®ne yam…ô m…®ne k…®sar…ô ye tahik. K…®m…®rkw…ôji …ôri…ô kas…ôpou. M…ôr…®g keinein norien yepou ye neram…® jir. In nar aparu. In rukwar k…®n nahasien m…®ne kakon…ô kape n…®mh…ôyen.\x - \xo 3:7-8 \xt Rom 3:13 \x*   
\p
\v 9 !Aweh! Neramtaw…ô, n…®p…®g k…®rik k…®taw…ô kamhani vi vi Kughen R…®mtaw…ô k…®n, m…®sarar, mamhani hah narmam…ô yame Kughen r…®mnor …ôri…ô kamhav…ôh nanm…®n.  
\v 10 Nher…® yermam…ô k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô ramni kwis n…®ni-vivi-yen m…®ne nahasien. Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô, nar e r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien.  
\v 11 ?Nak…®rkun m…ô nu heik…ôn m…®ne nu ouk…ôh to kr…ôs…®-p…ôn ye n…®mr…® nu k…®rikian…ô u…ô? N…®kam.  
\v 12 Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô. ?Nai e figtri to r…®ku…ô k…®n kw…ônwai nai e olif u…ô? N…®kam. ?K…®ni grep to r…®ku…ô k…®n kw…ônkwai nai e fig u…ô? N…®kam. K…®ni n…®mr…® nu ouk…ôh r…®p…ôh n…®kwar-kwarien k…®n nu heik…ôn.   
\s1 N…®rkunien yame rams…®-p…ôn tuk Kughen  
\p
\v 13 ?Kw…ôn k…®rik ye kwerkwan ir…ômi…ô yame r…®kin ram…ôs…®k m…ô r…®rkun p…®k nar u…ô? Rhuv…ô. P…ôh n…®mraghien huv…ô kafan tukramhajoun m…ô r…®rkun …ôfrak…®s nar. P…ôh in tukror nar…®mnar ye n…®rkunien, k…®ni p…ôh n…ôr…®gien kafan tukreiwaiyu.  
\v 14 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô r…®kimi…ô ramor p…®k jalus, u…ô naks…ôr…®g atuk …ôm…ô …ômi…ô, to nakhap…ôh n…®sausitien mham…ô nakharkun p…®k nar, tam…ô nakaseiku…ô atuk …ôm…ô ir…ômi…ô.  
\v 15 N…ôr…®gien has m…®n…ô a khap…ôh nhas…®-p…ônien ye rao ye neai; m…ôr…®g kape tokrei tan…ô …ôm…ô, m…®ne n…ôr…®gien kape yermam…ô, m…®ne kape Setan.  
\v 16 Meinai n…®p…®g narmam…ô kasor jalus, masorkeikei m…ô tukamhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk …ôri…ô, m…ôkneik…®n mas…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô kap…ôri…ô atuk n…ôr…®gien, masor nahasien, k…®ni norien has m…®n…ô fam kamhat…ôrhav-p…ô.   
\p
\v 17 M…ôr…®g yermam…ô yame rav…ôh n…®rkunien yame rams…®-p…ôn ye rao ye neai, kafan norien tukror m…ôkneik…®n: Nar yame ram…ôkup…ôn, kafan n…®mraghien tukratuatuk. K…®ni morkeikei p…®k n…ôm…ôrinuyen. In yem…ô mar k…®rik. In ramsiai narmam…ô. K…®ni in norkeikeiyen kafan tukreihu…ô. K…®ni n…®mraghien kafan tukr…®ku…ô k…®n kw…ônkwan r…®psaah. In tukr…ôm narmam…ô m…ô k…®s…ôm n…ômhen …ôm…ô. Tukr…®p…ôh n…®niyen nar k…®rik m…®p…ôh mamor nar p…®s…®n.  
\v 18 Narmam…ô kape n…ôr…ôhuyen n…ôm…ôrinuyen k…®s…ômhen k…®n narmam…ô yame kamhasuv kweru nai ye n…ôsimien, k…®ni rhakt…ô mamor kw…ônkwan. Tukm…ô k…®sasitu ye narmam…ô m…®s…ôr…ôhu n…ôm…ôrinuyen, norien kap…ôri…ô tukr…®ku…ô k…®n n…®mraghien yame in ratuatuk.\x - \xo 3:18 \xt Mat 5:9 \x*   
\c 4  
\s1 Yermam…ô yame rorkeikei p…®k norien kape tokrei tan…ô  
\p
\v 1 ?Naha e nhag…®n nuknei t…®goh m…®ne n…ômhokien ye n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô? Nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e kamhau…ô meinai k…®mi…ô naksorkeikei m…ô taks…ôr…®g huv…ô ye n…®praimi…ô. K…®ni n…ôt…ôr…®gien m…®n…ô a kape n…ôr…®gien huv…ô ye n…®praimi…ô, iri…ô kasoriah r…®kimi…ô k…®rikian…ô k…®rikian…ô.\x - \xo 4:1 \xt Rom 7:23 \x*  
\v 2 R…®kimi…ô ramv…ôn tuk nar…®mnar kape n…ôm…ô p…®s…®n m…®n…ô, m…ôr…®g nakhap…ôh nhav…ôhyen, k…®ni masotgoh mamhauh …ômi…ô m…®n…ô tuk nhav…ôhyen nar…®mnar. Naksorkeikei nar…®mnar t…®ks…®n, m…ôr…®g nakhap…ôh nhav…ôhyen, mashopni narmam…ô tukun. M…ôr…®g nakhap…ôh nhav…ôhyen nar…®mnar meinai nakhap…ôh n…®saiyohyen Kughen tukun.  
\v 3 K…®ni n…®p…®g tukm…ô naksaiyoh k…®n, mhap…ôh nhav…ôhyen, meinai n…®m…®saiyoh k…®n ye n…ôr…®gien yame rahas, mham…ô takhav…ôh …ôm…ô nar…®mnar kape n…ôr…®g-huv…ôyen ye n…®praimi…ô.   
\p
\v 4 !Aweh! N…®m…®s…ôp…ôh Kughen mhav…ôn mas…ôri-p…ôn norien kape tokrei tan…ô r…ômhen k…®n yame piraov…®n r…®p…ôh n…®siaiyen kafan yerman, m…ôp…ôh, mam…ôri-p…ôn yerman p…®s…®n. ?Nakharkun u…ô n…®kam, m…ô, yermam…ô yame rorkeikei nar…®mnar kape tokrei tan…ô in ram…ôm…ôk…®n Kughen? Yermam…ô a tukramorkeikei nar…®mnar kape tokrei tan…ô, in t…®km…®r kape Kughen.\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Rom 8:7; 1 Jon 2:15 \x*  
\v 5 Naksor m…ôknak…®n, masor t…ôkun n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen\f + \fr 4:5 \ft  Jemes ram…ôgkiar ye Ol Testamen, m…ôr…®g keinein m…ô ram…ôgkiar atuatuk ye naha japta u…ô ves.\f* yame ramni m…ô Nanm…®n kape Kughen yame ramar…ô yerkitaw…ô rorkeikei m…ô k…®taw…ô kafan m…®n…ô …ôm…ô.  
\v 6 M…ôr…®g Kughen ramaut…ô-p…ô k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen rehu…ô p…®k. Ror p…ôn N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúKughen tukr…ôtap…®g k…®n narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®sausit,  
\q2 m…ôr…®g tukraut…ô-p…ôn k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen k…®mi narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhaw…ôh-si-…ôhu kap…ôri…ô n…ôr…®gien.‚Äù\rq (Prov 3:34) \rq*\x - \xo 4:6 \xt 1 Pita 5:5\x*   
\p
\v 7 Ror m…ôkneik…®n, m…ô takas…ôkeikei mhav…ôh-si-…ôhu …ômi…ô m…®sor n…ôkwai Kughen. N…®p…®g Setan tukramu…ô m…®v…ôhsi-pre v…ôhsi-pre k…®mi …ômi…ô, taks…ôrer t…®m t…®m, p…ôh in tukrap m…®v…ôn isok tuk …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Efes 6:12 \x*  
\v 8 Hav…ôn ipak…ô tuk Kughen k…®ni In tukru…ô ipak…ô tuk …ômi…ô. K…®mi…ô yor t…ôvhag…ô has m…®n…ô, s…ôraov. K…®ni k…®mi…ô yam…ô m…®ne n…ôt…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô ramor k…®raru, sor n…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô ratuatuk.\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Aes 1:16; Sek 1:3; Mal 3:7 \x*  
\v 9 Rhuv…ô m…ô r…®kimi…ô tukr…ômh…ô k…®ni m…ôpou, m…®sas…ôk apomh tuk kap…ômi…ô t…ôvhag…ô has. Hap…ôh n…®sarhien, m…®sas…ôk …ôm…ô. P…ôh kap…ômi…ô nagienien tukr…®rk…ôk, r…®kimi…ô tukr…ôp…ôu.  
\v 10 Hav…ôhsi-…ôhu …ômi…ô mhau…ô tuk Kughen Yermaru, k…®ni In tukr…®v…ôh-si hakt…ô …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 4:10 \xt Job 5:11; 1 Pita 5:6 \x*   
\p
\v 11 Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô. Takhap…ôh nhani-oror-ien nhagmi…ô m…®n…ô. Tukm…ô yermam…ô k…®rik ramni-has nhag piauni, u…ô mamruk-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien has k…®rik iran, kw…ôn a in ramni hah loa kape Kughen,\f + \fr 4:11 \ft  ∆émru loa e ye Jem 1:15.\f* mamni m…ô loa e in nar apnap…®g, r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien. M…ôr…®g yermam…ô yame ramni m…ô loa e r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien, to r…®p…ôh norien n…ôkwan, mamor …ôm…ô m…ô in ramehu…ô ye loa.  
\v 12 M…ôr…®g Kughen p…®s…®n …ôm…ô In r…®mn…ôr…ôhu loa e. In p…®s…®n …ôm…ô tukr…ôkir narmam…ô. In p…®s…®n …ôm…ô r…®rkun n…®v…ôh-m…®raghien narmam…ô, m…®ne noriahyen. ?M…ôr…®g ik pa? ?Rhawor e nakm…ô tak…ôkir norien kape piam m…®n…ô?\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Rom 2:1; 14:4 \x*   
\s1 Taks…ôt…®gt…ô ye Kughen  
\p
\v 13 S…ôt…ôr…®g-ru. K…®mi…ô nakamhani mham…ô, ‚ÄúTowei u…ô tian…ôkwamer, khav…ôn apa ye taon k…®rik, m…®sar…ô aik…®n kape newk k…®rikian…ô, m…®sor bisnes aik…®n, mhav…ôh mane aik…®n.‚Äù  
\v 14 Naks…ôgkiar m…ôknak…®n, m…ôr…®g nakseinein naha nhag…®n yame tukr…®t…ôrhav tian…ôkwamer. ?K…®ni n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô in r…ômhen k…®n naha nhag…®n? In r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n nehenap yame ram…ônah, m…®rk…ôk m…®n.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Sam 39:5,11; Prov 27:1 \x*  
\v 15 M…ôr…®g rhuv…ô m…ô tukm…ô naks…ôgkiar, takhani m…ôkneik…®n mham…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô ye n…ôr…®gien …ôfrak…®s kape Kughen, k…®taw…ô tuksor nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a.‚Äù  
\v 16 M…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, naks…ôgkiar ausit mhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk …ômi…ô. N…ôgkiar-ausitien m…®n…ô m…ôknak…®n k…®sahas p…®k.  
\v 17 Ror m…ôkneik…®n m…ô yermam…ô yame r…®rkun norien nar yame ratuatuk, m…®p…ôh norien, ramor t…ôvhag…ô has en.\x - \xo 4:17 \xt Luk 12:47 \x*   
\c 5  
\s1 N…ôgkiarien ramv…ôn k…®mi narmam…ô kap…ôri…ô naut…ô rehu…ô  
\p
\v 1 K…®mi…ô narmam…ô kap…ômi…ô naut…ô rehu…ô. S…ôt…ôr…®g huv…ô k…®n n…ôgkiarien e. Rhuv…ô m…ô taks…ôr…®g rahas m…®sas…ôk apomh tuk nahasien yame tukru…ô tuk …ômi…ô.  
\v 2 Kap…ômi…ô naut…ô ru…ôm…ôt…®t ta, k…®ni …®vn m…®n…ô kw…ôs…ôkw…ôteih-…ôkw…ôteih kap…ômi…ô neip…ôn.\x - \xo 5:2 \xt Mat 6:19 \x*  
